name: SympatheticEar
0:
”Alexa, ask sympathetic ear to listen to me”
”Alexa, ask sympathetic ear can we have a chat”
”Alexa, ask sympathetic ear let me talk”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sympathetic ear
des: Whether it's to talk about a worry you have or just talk through a problem you are trying to solve. Sympathetic Ear is here to listen. Just as to be listened to. No judgement, no trying to fix you, just someone listening. Say Alexa, Open Sympathetic Ear.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
